name: Katya Solnce
description: Hello. My name is Ekaterina. I can tell, that I the usual girl which want I shall meet the man with which to have serious atudes, the family and it is possible children in the future. I done not interested with any games, I am interested only with serious atudes which will be under construction only on trust. Also I as well as many girls love the nature, flowers. My favourite flower is the tulip. Very interesting flower and I like to receive them from the friends if they present me it as a gift. I like to visit cinema, some cafes with friends. Sometimes I like to drink a few wine. After work I like to walk on park, to breathe fresh air.
